  "zones": {
    "A": {
      "name": "The Approach",
      "crystals": 4,
      "checkpoints": 1,
      "description": "Calm reprieve after The Gauntlet. Basic platforming with L1/L2 mechanics. Entry checkpoint only. Wide platforms, low hazard density — player catches breath."
    },
    "B": {
      "name": "The Convergence",
      "crystals": 6,
      "checkpoints": 1,
      "description": "Greatest-hits zone. Moving platforms (L2/L4) + key locks (L3) + spike corridors (L4). Checkpoint earned at midpoint after navigating the combined gauntlet. 3 keys (gold/red/blue) on detour platforms — all 3 required to open the vault."
    },
    "C": {
      "name": "The Sanctum Chamber",
      "crystals": 4,
      "checkpoints": 0,
      "description": "Single-path precision sequence. No checkpoint — this is the final run. Timed platform (MP-T1, 3s timer). 3-key vault at the end. Ambient lighting shifts to warm gold as player approaches the vault. Victory screen triggers on exit portal entry."
    }
  },
  "levelComplete": false,
  "notes": "Zone A: 4 crystals, entry checkpoint. Zone B: 6 crystals, midpoint checkpoint, 3 keys on detours. Zone C: 4 crystals, no checkpoint, 1 timed platform (MP-T1, 3s), 3-key vault. 70% gate (10/14). Timed platform disappears 3s after player first stands on it; respawn at last safe position. All 3 keys required to open vault. Ambient warm lighting shift in Zone C — visual payoff. Music: L4→L5 minor-to-major shift is the signature moment. L4→L5 transition should feel like earned relief."
